        <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">Find an agency supply teacher</h1>

        <p class="govuk-body">Use this service to:</p>

        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>find and hire a worker, using an agency</li>
          <li>create a shortlist of suppliers based on your needs and download or save it</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="govuk-body">You can use a separate service to find a managed service provider who can manage all your supply needs for you.</p>

        <a href="#" role="button" class="govuk-button govuk-button--start govuk-!-margin-top-2 govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
          Start now
        </a>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Before you start</h2>

        <p class="govuk-body">To use the service, you will need to register for an account and get login details.</p>

        <p class="govuk-body">You will also need to have:</p>

        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>your school's postcode, name or URN</li>
          <li>details of how long you will want the worker</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
